<h3 id="why-amsterdam-works-for-me">Why Amsterdam works for me</h3>
<p>To my surprise, when Dutch people from outside of the city tell me about Amsterdam, they usually assume Iâ€™m here for the culture and proximity to commercial innovation. Having grown up in the South of the Netherlands as a queer person of color, Iâ€™ve become intimately familiar with what it means to be The Other. Next to <a class="internal-link" href="/rotterdam">Rotterdam</a>, Amsterdam is the only place in the country that doesnâ€™t further cultivate that feeling. Itâ€™s been a healing experience for me to call this city home.</p>
